/build

# Release signing material — never commit. Back this up manually
# in a password manager / secure storage. Losing it = bricked
# updates on the tablet fleet (no Play Store fallback for our
# enterprise distribution).
# Ignore the contents of keystore/ but NOT the directory itself, so the
# next `!` rule can re-include the disaster-recovery README. Using
# `/keystore/` (a directory pattern) would short-circuit the negation.
/keystore/*
!/keystore/README.md
*.jks
*.keystore